0xE0000000 Kernel Heap
0xC0100000 Kernel Code (.text) 0xC0000000

Bit 31 12 11 9 8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0
Page Avail G PS A PCD Table PWT U/S P Addr
31-12: Page Table Base Address (4KB aligned) 8: G - Global (ignored if CR4.PGE=0) 7: PS - Page Size (0=4KB, 1=4MB) 6: A - Accessed 5,4: PCD/PWT - Cache controls 3: U/S - User/Supervisor (0=Ring0, 1=Ring3) 2: R/W - Read/Write (0=RO, 1=RW) 1: P - Present (1=mapped)
CPL = 3 (Current Privilege Level) PDE[0x48].U/S = 1 (User accessible) PTE[0x345].U/S = 1 (User accessible) Access PERMITTED
CPL = 3 (Current Privilege Level) PDE[0x300].U/S = 0 (Supervisor only) Page Fault (#PF) Error Code: P=1, U/S=1 (user access to supervisor page)
CPL = 0 (Current Privilege Level) PDE[0x300].U/S = 0 (Supervisor only) Access PERMITTED (CPL U/S)
